svg.title: Comparison of optical telescope primary mirrors
svg.desc: Comparison of nominal sizes of primary mirrors of notable optical telescopes compared with some other telescopes and objects, by CMG Lee. Dotted lines show mirrors with equivalent light-gathering ability. Thanks to user at 71.41.210.146 for data on holes in mirrors.
